FBIS3-35390 "drnes037_n_94002" FBIS-NES-94-037 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Feb 1994 LEBANON Army Warned Against Allowing Firing in South NC2402114794 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 1030 GMT 24 Feb 94 NC2402114794 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Citing security sources in the border zone, our military correspondent reports that the Lebanese Army has recently allowed firing in areas under its control or areas adjacent to its deployment zone. The security sources affirmed to our correspondent that any shooting directed at us will be returned, and this will expose the Lebanese Army troops to the possibility of being hit. The sources added that the Lebanese Army must take this into consideration.
